{"tid":2084031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"71 維園見，今晚十點一齊大叫","createTime":"2020-06-29T06:10:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T07:57:14.000Z","uid":52609,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"bc9983e228993d22df667c4b29d22d4e241518cc","tid":2084031,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:10:45.000Z","msg":"而家宣傳嘅成本愈嚟愈高，連儂牆都要快閃同地下化<br />\n但喺大家喺咪唔記得咗仲有兩個最低成本嘅宣傳方法：<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>大叫、Airdrop</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n今晚十點，一齊大叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n七一前晚晚都叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未返到屋企就Airdrop<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">七一！維園見！</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">七一！兩點！維園見！</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">七一！上街！抗惡法！</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港！時代革命！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/22QOB4g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F22QOB4g.jpg&h=a9f1780e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EnHtB4g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEnHtB4g.jpg&h=2f99f434&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hHODZhB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https:/